 its sticky saliva."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It has space in its throat to store saliva. It can also roll up its tongue and store it in the same spot."},{"version":"black","text":"The long tongue is always soggy with slobber. The saliva contains a solvent that causes numbness."},{"version":"white","text":"The long tongue is always soggy with slobber. The saliva contains a solvent that causes numbness."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Their saliva contains lots of components that can dissolve anything. The numbness caused by their lick does not dissipate."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Their saliva contains lots of components that can dissolve anything. The numbness caused by their lick does not dissipate."},{"version":"x","text":"It wraps things with its extensible tongue. Getting too close to it will leave you soaked with drool."},{"version":"y","text":"Their saliva contains lots of components that can dissolve anything. The numbness caused by their lick does not dissipate."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"It wraps things with its extensible tongue. Getting too close to it will leave you soaked with drool."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Their saliva contains lots of components that can dissolve anything. The numbness caused by their lick does not dissipate."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"A contest is under way to determine which one can stick its tongue out the farthest. The current record is...more than 82 feet."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It uses its tongue much more skillfully than its hands or its feet. It can deftly pick up a single small bean with its tongue."},{"version":"sword","text":"Lickilicky\u2019s strange tongue can stretch to many times the length of its body. No one has figured out how Lickilicky\u2019s tongue can stretch so far."},{"version":"shield","text":"Lickilicky can do just about anything with its tongue, which is as dexterous as the human hand. In contrast, Lickilicky\u2019s use of its fingers is clumsy."},{"version":